summary: Jasmine Patel is a 31-year-old woman who is 5'4". She works in the tech industry as a software engineer and studied at the University of California, Berkeley. Jasmine currently lives in Los Angeles, California, but is originally from San Francisco. She speaks English, Hindi, and Spanish. Jasmine values sustainability, authenticity, and lifelong learning. Some of her interests include hiking, living a green lifestyle, coding, playing the guitar, and cooking organic meals. She is a Hindu, has a liberal political inclination, and seeks a long-term relationship, though she is open to short-term as well. Jasmine identifies herself as straight and is interested in monogamy. Jasmine is of South Asian ethnicity and she hopes to have children in the future. She has a pet dog, an Aries, an 'INFJ' MBTI personality type, and does not consume any type of drugs or smoke, although she drinks occasionally. Jasmine leads an active lifestyle. She prefers a straight partner between the ages of 28 and 35 who doesn't smoke or take drugs, exercises regularly, hopes to have children, and drinks occasionally.
